Type: Package
Package: waspasR
Title: Tool Kit to Implement WASPAS Based Multi - Criteria Decision
    Analysis (MCDA) Solutions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Barbara", "Flavio", , "flavio.barbara@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Santos", "Marcos", , "marcosdossantos_doutorado_uff@yahoo.com.br", role = "ctb")
  )
Maintainer: Barbara Flavio <flavio.barbara@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a set of functions to implement decision - making
    systems based on the WASPAS method.  Set data of Alternatives, valued
    according to Weighted Criteria common to the alternatives.  These
    values must be continuous numeric. Thus, the entries are:
    Alternatives, Criteria, Weight of each criterion and flags that
    indicate whether the criterion is monotonic cost or monotonic benefit.
